::Kluster/Rex/Shredder::

"You're welcome," Kluster says absent mindedly, his mind sunk in the 
data he was looking over. He finally stops, pressing a button to 
clear the screen.

"Rex?" he says over his comm, "Can you report to my position?"

A few seconds later Rex walks in, looking at all the bots 
assembled. "Whoever sent that transmission you told me to get isn't 
replying," he says, frowning as he looks Shredder over.

"Allright," Kluster responds, "This bot just came in," he points to 
Whistler, "Help him with stuff he needs. Shredder, come with me. One 
of your group can come also, but I'd appreciate it if the rest went 
to guest quarters."

Shredder nods, turning to look at the ex-Destrons, "Anyone in 
particular want to come?"
